Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.13,0:00:43.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Time.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.63,0:00:47.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Space.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.38,0:00:50.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Reality.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.21,0:00:55.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's more than a linear path.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.88,0:01:04.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's a prism of endless possibility,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.84,0:01:10.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}where a single choice{\i0}\N{\i1}can branch out into infinite realities,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.05,0:01:16.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}creating alternate worlds{\i0}\N{\i1}from the ones you know.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.92,0:01:21.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I am the Watcher.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.51,0:01:26.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I am your guide{\i0}\N{\i1}through these vast new realities.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.26,0:01:31.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Follow me and ponder the question...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.34,0:01:36.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}"What if?"{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.92,0:01:52.80,Default,,0,0,0,,For the win. This is it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.59,0:01:57.22,Default,,0,0,0,,And this is it, for the win.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.80,0:02:01.09,Default,,0,0,0,,For the win. This is it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.17,0:02:03.46,Default,,0,0,0,,For the...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.26,0:02:07.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes! First try.\NJane, you owe me 50--
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.34,0:02:09.09,Default,,0,0,0,,-Uh... Oh! Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.17,0:02:10.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, Jane, Jane, Jane!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.96,0:02:12.71,Default,,0,0,0,,It's beeping! It's doing the beeping!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.13,0:02:16.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I need to talk\Nto the director of S.H.I.E.L.D.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.46,0:02:17.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Because, if my data is correct,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.05,0:02:19.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I believe an alien invasion\Nis imminent and...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.80,0:02:20.80,Default,,0,0,0,,-Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.26,0:02:25.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Two years ago, the same anomaly\Nstruck Star Alpha Icarus
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.13,0:02:27.71,Default,,0,0,0,,and the entire star dimmed\Nand then, poof, disintegrated.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.96,0:02:32.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I know this is the Parks Department,\Nbut isn't there something you can do?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.55,0:02:34.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Talking about the end of the world,\Nmy dude.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.80,0:02:41.63,Default,,0,0,0,,They're here.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.71,0:02:44.21,Default,,0,0,0,,We're too late. The invasion has begun.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.21,0:02:52.21,Default,,0,0,0,,-Holy moly!\N-Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.17,0:02:57.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Citizens of Midgard...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.42,0:03:02.71,Default,,0,0,0,,...your dull lives are about\Nto come to an end.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.80,0:03:05.09,Default,,0,0,0,,-Prepare yourselves...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.46,0:03:11.21,Default,,0,0,0,,for the party prince!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.59,0:03:17.59,Default,,0,0,0,,-This is gonna be awesome. Whoo!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.67,0:03:19.71,Default,,0,0,0,,More than battles won or lost,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.80,0:03:22.59,Default,,0,0,0,,it's relationships\Nthat truly define a hero.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.67,0:03:24.96,Default,,0,0,0,,The people who shape them, their stories.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.88,0:03:29.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Thor and Loki, a brotherhood{\i0}\N{\i1}so strong and pivotal,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.59,0:03:31.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}it would change the fate of a universe.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.71,0:03:36.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Their childhood taught Thor many lessons.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.30,0:03:38.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But in another universe,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.80,0:03:42.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}instead of raising the Jotunheim prince,{\i0}\N{\i1}Loki, as his own son,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.01,0:03:45.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Odin returned him to his people.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.42,0:03:49.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Without his trickster brother{\i0}\N{\i1}to keep things, let's say, lively,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.42,0:03:52.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Thor grew into a very different prince.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.71,0:04:00.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Rest, my love.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.17,0:04:04.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Allow the Odinsleep to restore\Nyour body and soul.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.76,0:04:20.30,Default,,0,0,0,,He's asleep. And, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.38,0:04:23.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm off to my sister's\Nto celebrate the solstice.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.55,0:04:27.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, this is your first taste of kinghood,\Nmy prince.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.13,0:04:28.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I expect you to study,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.51,0:04:31.01,Default,,0,0,0,,read up on the Nine Realms\Nthat you will one day rule.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.09,0:04:32.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course, Mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.30,0:04:34.22,Default,,0,0,0,,-No parties.\N-Of course, Mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.30,0:04:36.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Remember,\NHeimdall will be watching.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.17,0:04:40.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, what? You can't be serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.38,0:04:41.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Behave.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.46,0:04:49.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Heimdall, there you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.26,0:04:53.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Just off to study.\NBooks won't read themselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.76,0:04:55.05,Default,,0,0,0,,But your mother said--
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.13,0:04:56.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be such a wet blanket, Hogun.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.84,0:04:59.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, guys, stop. My father has\Nruled Asgard for centuries.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.88,0:05:02.67,Default,,0,0,0,,And, look, the most interesting thing\Nthat he's ever done is fall asleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.76,0:05:06.76,Default,,0,0,0,,He only cares about duty\Nand blah-blah-blah-blah responsibility.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.84,0:05:09.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I'm not gonna be like him, right?\NThe boring king? Uh-uh.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.34,0:05:16.67,Default,,0,0,0,,But Heimdall sees all.\NIf we try anything, he'll call Frigga.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.76,0:05:18.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, ye of little faith.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.34,0:05:20.51,Default,,0,0,0,,We are going to the most backward,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.59,0:05:23.76,Default,,0,0,0,,backwater planet that not even\NHeimdall pays attention to.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.84,0:05:25.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Alert the realms.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.76,0:05:29.51,Default,,0,0,0,,-Party on Midgard!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.59,0:05:31.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.21,0:05:32.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Huzzah!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.63,0:05:35.05,Default,,0,0,0,,To Thor, the party prince!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.13,0:05:37.21,Default,,0,0,0,,-Welcome! Welcome, friends.\N-Party prince!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.30,0:05:38.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Enjoy the night.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.71,0:05:39.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Thunder hug.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.05,0:05:43.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Here, have a drink.\NIt never runs out.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.46,0:05:47.29,Default,,0,0,0,,You try to drink it all,\Nbut you can't because it's magic! Huzzah!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.38,0:05:51.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Huzzah!\NThor! Thor! Thor! Thor! Thor!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.30,0:05:54.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Hollywood movies did not\Nprepare me for this.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.05,0:05:58.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Shouldn't there be more lasers?\NProbing? A flying cow?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.46,0:05:59.54,Default,,0,0,0,,According to my data,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.63,0:06:02.80,Default,,0,0,0,,the first extraterrestrial\Nto arrive was...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.88,0:06:04.67,Default,,0,0,0,,-Him?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.88,0:06:13.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh. I expected him to look more like...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.46,0:06:17.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Like what? E.T.? And less like\Na hottie McScotty, beach body Ken,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.17,0:06:20.71,Default,,0,0,0,,old-school Abercrombie catalog?\NI could go on. Let me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.80,0:06:21.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna go talk to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.01,0:06:23.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna make first contact\Nwith an alien.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.84,0:06:26.26,Default,,0,0,0,,First? I think half the Strip\Nbeat you to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.34,0:06:27.92,Default,,0,0,0,,You can make first contact with...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.01,0:06:30.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know, that guy.\NHe looks like a loser.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.42,0:06:32.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Ha! Big talk coming from a brunette.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.51,0:06:35.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going. How do I look?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.67,0:06:38.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Completely unprepared\Nfor whatever happens next.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.46,0:06:39.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, do me, do me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.46,0:06:44.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, you do me.\NYou do me, and you too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.34,0:06:47.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, you guys really get me. Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.88,0:06:49.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.42,0:06:52.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, there you are, all the way down there.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.17,0:06:54.59,Default,,0,0,0,,So tiny, I almost stood on you.\NHow are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.67,0:06:57.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Dr. Jane Foster of Earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.21,0:06:59.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, Thor, Crown Prince of Asgard.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.46,0:07:02.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, libations, crudité, baked goods?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.17,0:07:04.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Mmm. Topaz, what do I always say?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.38,0:07:05.55,Default,,0,0,0,,-I love cake.\N-Mmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.84,0:07:07.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, wait, wait. You're Thor?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.76,0:07:10.39,Default,,0,0,0,,As in Thor, the Norse god of thunder?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.46,0:07:14.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know anything about horse gods,\Nbut I do know how to bring the thunder.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.84,0:07:17.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh... Okay, moving on.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.51,0:07:20.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Eighteen months ago,\NAlpha Star Icarus died.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.51,0:07:22.14,Default,,0,0,0,,The astronomaly that preceded it...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.21,0:07:24.25,Default,,0,0,0,,-...happened again tonight.\N-Don't drink too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.34,0:07:26.05,Default,,0,0,0,,-Or too little.\N-Hey, thunder boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.13,0:07:28.26,Default,,0,0,0,,What I'm asking is, was that you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.34,0:07:32.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, Alpha Star.\NNow, that was an excellent party.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.09,0:07:34.09,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, we lost Fandral for three days.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.17,0:07:36.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Found him in a barn,\Ncurled up next to a baby goat.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.01,0:07:38.89,Default,,0,0,0,,It was classic. Isn't that right, Fandral?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.96,0:07:40.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I named him Gary.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.96,0:07:42.29,Default,,0,0,0,,-Yeah, you did.\N-Yeah, goats!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.38,0:07:43.63,Default,,0,0,0,,You killed a planet.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.71,0:07:46.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, what is that light box thing\Nyou've got there?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.51,0:07:49.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, it's magic. I love magic.\NDid you build this all by yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.38,0:07:52.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me? I happen to be\Nan astrophysicist with multiple PhDs.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.96,0:07:56.38,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, it would take a whole\Nteam of Asgardians to create such a thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.46,0:07:59.63,Default,,0,0,0,,You must be a genius.\NYou are a genius, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.71,0:08:02.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I don't know\Nabout genius, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.38,0:08:03.88,Default,,0,0,0,,-And your eyes...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.96,0:08:07.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Do all geniuses have such deep, dark eyes?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.42,0:08:10.63,Default,,0,0,0,,It's like watching the birth of two stars\Non the edge of the galaxy.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.71,0:08:12.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.21,0:08:17.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, it's happy hour.\NWant some half-price nachos?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.13,0:08:20.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, fine, Duck. But this is not a date.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.13,0:08:21.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's just see where this evolves.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.46,0:08:34.71,Default,,0,0,0,,-Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.80,0:08:35.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Release the foam.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.55,0:08:41.26,Default,,0,0,0,,-Blow on these.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.34,0:08:42.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Momma needs a brand-new eye.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.21,0:08:54.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Volstagg has crashed!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.09,0:08:56.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I now pronounce you Darcy and the Duck.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.26,0:08:57.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Uh-huh{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.13,0:09:21.55,Default,,0,0,0,,-Ah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.55,0:09:24.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.67,0:09:36.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, phone... Phone! Oh, shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.09,0:09:40.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr. Jane Foster?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.51,0:09:42.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Coming. I'm coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.84,0:09:44.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr. Jane Foster!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.71,0:09:46.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold on.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.46,0:09:48.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr. Jane Foster,\Nthis is S.H.I.E.L.D.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.92,0:09:53.30,Default,,0,0,0,,If you do not answer, we will--
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.38,0:09:54.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.88,0:09:55.88,Default,,0,0,0,,We have her, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.96,0:09:58.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Maria Hill,\NActing Director of S.H.I.E.L.D.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.30,0:09:59.68,Default,,0,0,0,,-You need to come with us.\N-Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.96,0:10:04.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Can this wait until after breakfast?\N'Cause...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.13,0:10:08.30,Default,,0,0,0,,You were the first to warn us\Nabout this extraterrestrial threat.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.38,0:10:11.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Now I hope you will be the key\Nto eliminating it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.71,0:10:14.71,Default,,0,0,0,,"Threat"? Would you call him\Na threat, really?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.80,0:10:18.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you wanna know why I am\Nthe Acting Director, Dr. Foster?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.80,0:10:20.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Nope.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.13,0:10:24.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Spicoli. This might be your party,\Nbut this isn't your planet.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.84,0:10:26.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Before someone gets hurt, I need...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.67,0:10:27.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Ball cannons!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.38,0:10:32.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.51,0:10:34.43,Default,,0,0,0,,-Is he okay?\N-He's still unconscious.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.09,0:10:37.22,Default,,0,0,0,,We getting food?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.30,0:10:38.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you have company, Dr. Foster?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.92,0:10:40.46,Default,,0,0,0,,-Uh... A friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.55,0:10:43.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Guys, guys, look.\NThere's a cute little rabbit in the sink.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.30,0:10:46.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, look at this little rabbit.\NIt's gorgeous.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.17,0:10:49.00,Default,,0,0,0,,He's... a zoologist. I'll call you, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.96,0:10:53.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I told you everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.46,0:10:55.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I followed the anomaly's origin to Vegas.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.67,0:10:57.09,Default,,0,0,0,,And then what did you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.17,0:11:00.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Um... Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.46,0:11:02.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Director, the party atmosphere\Nseems to be spreading.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.01,0:11:07.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Canada, Mongolia,\Neven Pennsylvania Dutch country.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.09,0:11:10.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Led by the main instigator,\NThor of Asgard,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.26,0:11:11.76,Default,,0,0,0,,who's now taken to the skies.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.84,0:11:14.13,Default,,0,0,0,,What? He left?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.21,0:11:17.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Did he... Did he even leave a note at...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.84,0:11:21.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, did...\NDid he say where he was going?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.13,0:11:22.63,Default,,0,0,0,,-Smooth.\N-Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.71,0:11:24.25,Default,,0,0,0,,-Sarcasm.\N-Paris.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.34,0:11:28.26,Default,,0,0,0,,One of his compatriots was,\Nand I quote, "jonesing for crêpes."
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.34,0:11:29.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Ma'am...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.80,0:11:32.38,Default,,0,0,0,,the last resort has arrived.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.46,0:11:35.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa, whoa.\N"Last resort" sounds very final.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.59,0:11:38.38,Default,,0,0,0,,This is Earth's first encounter\Nwith alien life.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.46,0:11:41.34,Default,,0,0,0,,How we respond today will set the tone\Nfor diplomatic relations
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.42,0:11:43.34,Default,,0,0,0,,between our worlds for generations.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.42,0:11:47.67,Default,,0,0,0,,"Diplomatic relations"?\NIs that what the kids are calling it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.76,0:11:48.89,Default,,0,0,0,,You're wrong, Doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.96,0:11:51.71,Default,,0,0,0,,This isn't S.H.I.E.L.D.'s\Nfirst alien rodeo.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.67,0:11:56.38,Default,,0,0,0,,A beeper? My dad has one!\NHe's a podiatrist.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.46,0:11:58.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, are you guys calling a podiatrist?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.63,0:12:02.63,Default,,0,0,0,,It's done.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.26,0:12:07.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it happening? Did it happen?\NWhat'd I miss?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.01,0:12:09.80,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, here we go. Nestle on in.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.88,0:12:12.71,Default,,0,0,0,,-Everyone say "waffles." I love that word.\N-Cheese.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.80,0:12:14.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Waffles with maple syrup\Nand whipped cream on top.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.96,0:12:15.96,Default,,0,0,0,,-Thor!\N-Thor!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.05,0:12:17.43,Default,,0,0,0,,He came! He's here!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.92,0:12:22.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Oi! Where's that son of a witch,\NThor Odinson?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.21,0:12:25.13,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.21,0:12:30.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Fandral, tell me, is that butt-ugly\Npopsicle stick talking to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.59,0:12:41.51,Default,,0,0,0,,-Bring it on in.\N-I can't believe you came!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.59,0:12:43.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Loki, you are the absolute best!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.76,0:12:45.76,Default,,0,0,0,,You're my brother\Nfrom another mother, man. I mean that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.84,0:12:47.63,Default,,0,0,0,,-I mean it.\N-Brothers forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.71,0:12:49.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Brothers forever!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.63,0:12:50.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Forever!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.30,0:12:54.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, what's that boom? Did you boom?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.71,0:12:56.59,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I didn't boom.\NDid you boom? You always boom.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.67,0:12:59.05,Default,,0,0,0,,-I never boom. I only boom in private.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.13,0:13:02.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, oh, oh. Loki, look,\Nit's a shooting star. Make a wish, quick!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.63,0:13:05.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, yes, a shooting star.\NYes, okay. I wish... I wish...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.80,0:13:09.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I wish, I wish, I wish... I wish...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.67,0:13:13.84,Default,,0,0,0,,-Uh... I've got it!\N-What is it? Tell me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.92,0:13:16.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I couldn't possibly tell you.\NIt'll ruin the magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.71,0:13:17.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.13,0:13:29.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Whitesnake. We need to chat.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.13,0:13:34.63,Default,,0,0,0,,The name is Thor, with a "T"\Nand an "R" and an "O" and a "H."
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.71,0:13:35.84,Default,,0,0,0,,But not in that order.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.92,0:13:38.59,Default,,0,0,0,,-Quite some party you're throwing.\N-Isn't it the best?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.67,0:13:41.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, I'd hoped the Ice Bros would show,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.13,0:13:43.09,Default,,0,0,0,,but Loki himself? Prince Loki?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.17,0:13:45.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you kidding?\NI wouldn't miss this for the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.51,0:13:48.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen, bud, clean up this mess\Nand leave this planet.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.51,0:13:51.18,Default,,0,0,0,,What? No, I like it here.\NEveryone likes me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.26,0:13:53.51,Default,,0,0,0,,We're having a great time...\Ntill you showed up.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.59,0:13:55.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Party's over, pal.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.42,0:14:00.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Mmm. Yeah, maybe here's a thought.\NUh, how about you just buzz off?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.76,0:14:05.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.42,0:14:13.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I wasn't asking, hotshot.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.92,0:14:18.63,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, there's a Midgardian word\Nfor women like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.38,0:14:21.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Party pooper.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.51,0:14:24.39,Default,,0,0,0,,There. I said it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.46,0:14:26.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, this one's for Fury.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.42,0:14:32.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, for the rest of you...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.92,0:14:42.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Have at you!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.92,0:14:45.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Smooth move, bro. You just--
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.21,0:14:46.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Hammerang. Get it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.92,0:14:49.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Look, pal, I'm gonna count to three
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.30,0:14:51.05,Default,,0,0,0,,and you're gonna put the hammer down.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.80,0:14:55.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, here we go. Here we go.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.51,0:15:01.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, what did I tell you? Knock it off.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.17,0:15:22.75,Default,,0,0,0,,-Whoa.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.55,0:15:25.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, quit it. These are...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.01,0:15:29.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know what these are. No one does.\NBut... No! I said no! Stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.96,0:15:33.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, but I just have to do a little boop.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.26,0:15:45.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, no, your weird rocks\Nhave all fallen over.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.80,0:15:47.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Boo-hoo-hoo-hoo.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.01,0:15:53.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.59,0:16:03.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Party foul.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.51,0:16:09.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Be right with you. Just one second.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.13,0:16:13.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, there it is. Whoo! Let's do this.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.71,0:16:54.84,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, I'm starting to...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.92,0:16:56.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Ow! Not the hair!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.38,0:17:43.38,Default,,0,0,0,,You know what you need?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.46,0:17:45.88,Default,,0,0,0,,A stiff drink and two weeks in Hawaii?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.96,0:17:47.17,Default,,0,0,0,,A time-out.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.26,0:17:50.47,Default,,0,0,0,,My mother punished me with time-outs\Nall the time, but I never learned a thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.55,0:17:54.76,Default,,0,0,0,,But maybe they'll work on you\Nbecause you're a party pooper.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.84,0:17:57.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, look, everyone! A party pooper.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.38,0:18:00.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Pooper! Pooper! Pooper!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.30,0:18:07.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Fury said you were the best.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.21,0:18:10.38,Default,,0,0,0,,That your punch was equal\Nto ten nuclear bombs.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.46,0:18:12.71,Default,,0,0,0,,That your cat could devour whole armies.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.80,0:18:14.84,Default,,0,0,0,,You've got a cat? What's its name?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.92,0:18:15.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Goose.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.05,0:18:18.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, {\i1}Top Gun!{\i0} You're Maverick!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.17,0:18:20.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Is your ego writing checks\Nthat your skills can't cash?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.59,0:18:21.67,Default,,0,0,0,,-No.\N-Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.34,0:18:24.76,Default,,0,0,0,,-Who are you?\N-Darcy. Big fan.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.84,0:18:27.47,Default,,0,0,0,,By the way, totally thought\Nyou were gonna be a dude captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.55,0:18:29.47,Default,,0,0,0,,But look at you, all not.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.55,0:18:32.76,Default,,0,0,0,,If I exert my full powers,\NI blow a crater in this planet.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.84,0:18:36.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Taking down Kappa Kappa frat freak\Nwon't be worth the fatalities.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.13,0:18:37.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Ooh. What about South Dakota?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.01,0:18:39.64,Default,,0,0,0,,-Or North Dakota?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.71,0:18:42.42,Default,,0,0,0,,-Uh... I need to get this.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.51,0:18:45.51,Default,,0,0,0,,So, uh, do you need an intern?\NCat wrangler?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.59,0:18:47.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Darcy, right now,\Nyou're running at an eight,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.84,0:18:49.67,Default,,0,0,0,,and I need you to take it down to a four.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.76,0:18:51.14,Default,,0,0,0,,-Okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.21,0:18:52.38,Default,,0,0,0,,-Hello?\N-{\i1}Jane!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.46,0:18:54.29,Default,,0,0,0,,-Hey!\N-When can I see you again?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.38,0:18:57.42,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the nicest, prettiest\NMidgardian woman I've ever met.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.51,0:18:59.30,Default,,0,0,0,,How many Earth women have you met?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.38,0:19:01.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, two. But the other one\Nhit me with a bridge
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.38,0:19:03.01,Default,,0,0,0,,and, well, that hurt more than my face.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.42,0:19:07.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Thor, be honest with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.59,0:19:11.30,Default,,0,0,0,,At your last party on Alpha Star,\Ndid you really destroy that planet?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.38,0:19:14.34,Default,,0,0,0,,No, no, it was more of a meteor anyway,\Nnot a planet.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.42,0:19:17.30,Default,,0,0,0,,And it was burning apart,\Nso we just kinda helped it along and...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.38,0:19:18.51,Default,,0,0,0,,So no one got hurt?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.59,0:19:19.88,Default,,0,0,0,,-Of course not.\N-Dr. Foster?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.96,0:19:22.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Even the baby goat, Gary, got home safely.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.30,0:19:23.72,Default,,0,0,0,,-Eventually.\N-Dr. Foster.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.80,0:19:25.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, I gotta go. Love you. Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.84,0:19:27.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.01,0:19:30.18,Default,,0,0,0,,What were we talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.26,0:19:32.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Look, all I'm saying is,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.13,0:19:34.71,Default,,0,0,0,,no one would notice\Nif you blew up a Dakota.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.80,0:19:36.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Honestly, I can't tell them apart.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.30,0:19:37.84,Default,,0,0,0,,South Dakota is on the bottom.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.92,0:19:39.13,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not a bad idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.21,0:19:41.00,Default,,0,0,0,,The Mojave Desert could withstand the hit.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.09,0:19:43.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Lure him to Siberia\Nand then go kaboom on his ass.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.13,0:19:47.96,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not serious.\NWe're not gonna kaboom him.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.05,0:19:49.63,Default,,0,0,0,,We're talking about the fate\Nof the planet.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.71,0:19:52.92,Default,,0,0,0,,He's a lughead, sure, and far from\Nthe brightest crayon in the box.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.01,0:19:57.26,Default,,0,0,0,,But this plan is way over the top,\Nand I refuse to let it happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.34,0:20:00.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for your expertise, Dr. Foster,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.55,0:20:03.34,Default,,0,0,0,,but your assistance is no longer required.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.46,0:20:09.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn! There goes my internship\Nwith the Galactic Queen Bee.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.63,0:20:14.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, look who came waddling back.\NMrs. the Duck.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.67,0:20:17.05,Default,,0,0,0,,-Not now, Howard!\N-Hello, Thor?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.13,0:20:18.88,Default,,0,0,0,,-Who's this?\N{\i1}-It's Jane. Can you hear me?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.96,0:20:22.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait. Is this the girl?\NThor's new sweet lady? Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.34,0:20:23.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Is Thor there?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.46,0:20:27.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Late-night Chinese is the best.\NOh, I love food.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.34,0:20:30.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Loki, get your blue butt over here.\NYou have to try these dumplings.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.30,0:20:33.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Earth girl.\NYou haven't got a friend, have you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.55,0:20:35.34,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, we could double date.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.42,0:20:38.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Ugh! Will you just put him on the phone?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.17,0:20:40.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, don't get your knickers in a twist.\NHe's right here... Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.17,0:20:46.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh. Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.26,0:20:47.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello? Loki?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.05,0:20:51.13,Default,,0,0,0,,-Hey, hey. Watch the feathers.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.21,0:20:53.67,Default,,0,0,0,,-Too bad we can't call his mom.\N-What?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.76,0:20:54.89,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what always happens.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.96,0:20:57.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Teenagers throw a party,\Nit gets out of control...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.26,0:20:59.18,Default,,0,0,0,,-Oh, you really are a genius.\N-Whoa.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.26,0:21:02.51,Default,,0,0,0,,It's really starting to look that way,\Nisn't it? What'd I say?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.59,0:21:05.05,Default,,0,0,0,,If there's a Thor and a Loki,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.13,0:21:09.55,Default,,0,0,0,,then there must be an Odin\Nand a Frigga and a Heimdall!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.63,0:21:10.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, he-man-who-now?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.71,0:21:20.29,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, I've got a crown too,\Nand we both like fire, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.38,0:21:22.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on. Let's see you turn up\Nthe heat on this thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.67,0:21:25.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh... Ooh, look at the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.34,0:21:33.42,Default,,0,0,0,,How low can I go?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.09,0:21:42.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone! Watch me slide down\Nthat pointy thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.13,0:21:47.13,Default,,0,0,0,,And away!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.42,0:21:51.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoo!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.55,0:22:06.97,Default,,0,0,0,,This one goes here. Green in the thing.\NOkay, sweet. Good to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.05,0:22:08.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Selvig, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.21,0:22:11.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Re-aligning the satellites,\Nmagnifying the signal.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.46,0:22:15.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Heimdall!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.34,0:22:20.26,Default,,0,0,0,,-It's not working.\N-Okay, okay. My turn. I got this.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.34,0:22:23.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Would the owner of the navy blue Prius...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.21,0:22:41.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi. So, uh, about Thor...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.09,0:22:51.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Not cool. I actually felt that one.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.84,0:22:58.88,Default,,0,0,0,,-We're in position.\N-Arm the nukes.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.96,0:23:01.00,Default,,0,0,0,,What? But I thought she was the nuke.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.09,0:23:03.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Just in case she gets distracted by a cat.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.17,0:23:09.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh... Hello, Mrs. Odinwife?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.67,0:23:12.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, is that Chardonnay?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.51,0:23:15.30,Default,,0,0,0,,A varietal, yes. Can I help you?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.38,0:23:18.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Why do you insist on crushing my mellow?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.13,0:23:20.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Loosen up. Have fun. Smile a little.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.80,0:23:23.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Ready to fire on your command.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.30,0:23:25.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Fire in five...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.26,0:23:28.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I gave you a warning.\NHell, I gave you a warning punch.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.67,0:23:31.34,Default,,0,0,0,,-Four.\N-It's Thor. He's in trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.34,0:23:35.09,Default,,0,0,0,,-Three.\N-He's on Earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.09,0:23:37.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Two.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.96,0:23:40.88,Default,,0,0,0,,-What about Captain Marvel?\N-She'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.96,0:23:42.46,Default,,0,0,0,,One.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.63,0:23:50.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Thor, Crown Prince of Asgard,\Nonly son of Odin, what are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.76,0:23:52.09,Default,,0,0,0,,-Mother!\N-Mother?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.17,0:23:53.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Mother?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.30,0:23:54.63,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.71,0:23:57.63,Default,,0,0,0,,You must be using a lot of dark magic\Njust to check in on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.71,0:24:01.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Ugh, I had a visitor.\NShe's worried about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.26,0:24:03.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Wha... Jane sold me out?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.71,0:24:05.54,Default,,0,0,0,,She said you were on Midgard.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.63,0:24:07.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, she is mistaken.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.42,0:24:10.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm obviously in my room, studying.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.80,0:24:17.38,Default,,0,0,0,,-Do not tell falsehoods to your mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.46,0:24:21.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, you mean Earth.\NSorry, I misunderstood.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.67,0:24:24.80,Default,,0,0,0,,The locals call it that.\NYes, right. Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.88,0:24:26.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Confused there for a moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.51,0:24:30.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Me and my study group came down here\Nfor a cultural exchange.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.01,0:24:33.39,Default,,0,0,0,,"Cultural exchange."
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.46,0:24:35.71,Default,,0,0,0,,You know us. We're warriors for knowledge.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.80,0:24:39.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm. Really?\NThen this I have to see for myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.51,0:24:41.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm cutting my trip short.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.46,0:24:42.75,Default,,0,0,0,,You're coming here?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.84,0:24:48.47,Default,,0,0,0,,And, my sweet son, I expect to see\Nyour full syllabus when I arrive.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.84,0:24:51.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Now or never, Hill.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.84,0:24:53.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Stand down. We're done here.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.55,0:24:56.18,Default,,0,0,0,,We never get to fire the nukes.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:56.26,0:24:57.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I almost feel bad for you, Blondie.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:58.05,0:25:00.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, you must help me.\NMy mother is coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:01.05,0:25:04.72,Default,,0,0,0,,My suggestion? Start in the corners,\Nclean your way outward.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:07.09,0:25:08.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Corners, corners...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:08.26,0:25:10.30,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's a sphere.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:11.26,0:25:15.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Ugh. Excuse me, ladies. I'm sorry,\Nbut I must leave early. Again.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:17.59,0:25:19.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Loki, my brother.\NI require your assistance.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:20.05,0:25:22.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, one step ahead of you, Tiny Thunder.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:22.38,0:25:25.71,Default,,0,0,0,,My bro's trying this thing in St. Louis.\NSaint... Is it "Louie"?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:25.80,0:25:27.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, we're about to make
Dialogue: 0,0:25:27.46,0:25:29.92,Default,,0,0,0,,-this universe's greatest slingshot.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:30.01,0:25:32.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Try to enjoy\Nthe rest of your time here.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:32.13,0:25:34.71,Default,,0,0,0,,See you in another thousand years.\NHeimdall.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:36.26,0:25:40.22,Default,,0,0,0,,No more slingshots. No more destruction.\NWe need to clean this mess up and go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:42.17,0:25:43.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Ugh! Now!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:44.84,0:25:47.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Ha!\NNice one. Almost fell for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:48.05,0:25:50.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not joking. My mother is coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:57.13,0:25:58.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:58.21,0:25:59.71,Default,,0,0,0,,But she's not my mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:59.80,0:26:02.30,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, I'm your brother\Nfrom another mother, remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:02.38,0:26:04.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, Ice Bros, let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:04.92,0:26:06.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait. You can't leave. Look at this place.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:06.84,0:26:09.34,Default,,0,0,0,,We have a duty to this planet.\NYou need to clean it up.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:09.42,0:26:12.13,Default,,0,0,0,,"Duty, clean"? Ugh, you sound like Odin.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:12.21,0:26:13.29,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:13.38,0:26:14.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Ice Men, let's bounce.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:18.38,0:26:20.13,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, listen, party's over.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:20.21,0:26:23.21,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't have to go home,\Nbut you can't stay.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:23.30,0:26:25.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, where you going? Come back.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:25.26,0:26:26.39,Default,,0,0,0,,No, no, no, no, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:26.46,0:26:29.46,Default,,0,0,0,,You do have to stay here,\Nand we need to clean up.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:29.55,0:26:31.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Look who's pooping the party now.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:31.84,0:26:34.38,Default,,0,0,0,,It is you! You are pooping the party.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:34.46,0:26:35.84,Default,,0,0,0,,-Where you going? Come back!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:35.92,0:26:38.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go, Topaz.\NWe shall ride like the wind.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:38.30,0:26:39.59,Default,,0,0,0,,-Please! Wait.\N-Loser.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:39.67,0:26:41.30,Default,,0,0,0,,And we're keeping the scoot-scoots.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:41.38,0:26:44.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Guys, please. Help, I...\NYou. How about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:44.71,0:26:47.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh... I think I hear my dad calling.\NGood luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:53.30,0:26:57.55,Default,,0,0,0,,People. Beings.\NPlease, everyone, you must stay and help.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:00.42,0:27:02.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Allfather, give me strength.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:08.38,0:27:10.34,Default,,0,0,0,,You will listen to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:12.30,0:27:14.13,Default,,0,0,0,,My mother is coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:14.21,0:27:18.00,Default,,0,0,0,,-Frigga?\N-And she is not happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:18.09,0:27:20.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Like, at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:20.30,0:27:21.59,Default,,0,0,0,,She's really mad.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:38.13,0:27:39.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, baby.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:02.17,0:28:03.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Thor.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:05.26,0:28:09.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, hello, Mother. Good to see you.\NWelcome to our study group.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:09.17,0:28:11.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:11.09,0:28:13.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone say hello to Mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:13.09,0:28:14.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello, Mother Frigga.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:14.80,0:28:17.51,Default,,0,0,0,,And to end our studies,\Nwhat do we always say, class?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:17.59,0:28:19.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Learning is magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:20.80,0:28:24.38,Default,,0,0,0,,See? I told you I was on an educational\Nand cultural exchange.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:24.46,0:28:27.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you know that Midgard\Nis the birthplace of the Snuggie?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:29.88,0:28:32.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Mother, you doubt?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:34.13,0:28:36.38,Default,,0,0,0,,But look at all this learning, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:43.63,0:28:46.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Thor, here's the information\Nyou requested on human civilizations.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:46.96,0:28:50.88,Default,,0,0,0,,And I loaded a few documentaries,\NPBS specials, NPR podcasts.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:50.96,0:28:52.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll call you next week to discuss it.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:52.71,0:28:58.29,Default,,0,0,0,,So tiny yet contains so, so much.\NThank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:58.38,0:29:00.51,Default,,0,0,0,,You must be Frigga. I'm Captain Marvel.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:00.59,0:29:05.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I know who you are.\NThank you for helping educate my son.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:05.38,0:29:07.01,Default,,0,0,0,,-Let's go, darling.\N-Wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:07.09,0:29:09.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Almost forgot.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:12.30,0:29:14.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:14.13,0:29:15.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Mother, I can explain.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:25.13,0:29:26.80,Default,,0,0,0,,-Hi.\N-Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:26.88,0:29:28.51,Default,,0,0,0,,You called my mother on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:28.59,0:29:30.17,Default,,0,0,0,,That wasn't a cool thing to do,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:30.26,0:29:33.09,Default,,0,0,0,,but it was the right thing. So, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:34.67,0:29:35.92,Default,,0,0,0,,You're welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:36.01,0:29:38.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll call you? Cools?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:38.51,0:29:40.47,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it is not "cools."
Dialogue: 0,0:29:40.55,0:29:41.76,Default,,0,0,0,,No?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:41.84,0:29:44.80,Default,,0,0,0,,But I thought we had something.\NI really like you, Jane.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:44.88,0:29:47.96,Default,,0,0,0,,And not just because you're a genius.\NYou're also very attractive and...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:48.55,0:29:50.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, then, ask me out on a date.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:50.30,0:29:51.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:51.80,0:29:55.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Jane Foster, it would be my honor\Nto take you on a date.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:55.71,0:30:00.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Before you answer, let me say that\NI know a whole planet full of unicorns.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:00.88,0:30:02.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Even the waiters are unicorns...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:02.63,0:30:05.42,Default,,0,0,0,,-It's wonderful.\N-Sounds delightful. Pick me up at00?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:16.34,0:30:19.76,Default,,0,0,0,,A world restored,\Nlove blossoming.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:19.84,0:30:24.01,Default,,0,0,0,,As children,\Nboth human and Asgardian, say,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:24.09,0:30:27.92,Default,,0,0,0,,together, they lived happily ever after.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:29.01,0:30:30.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, what?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:30.09,0:30:31.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:35.38,0:30:39.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, dear.\NPerhaps I spoke too soon.
